{"id":"api/forms/FormControlStatus","title":"FormControlStatus","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/forms\", \"name\": \"@angular/forms\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/forms/FormControlStatus\", \"name\": \"FormControlStatus\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/forms\">@angular/forms</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/model/abstract_model.ts#L50-L66\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"formcontrolstatus\">FormControlStatus<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/FormControlStatus#formcontrolstatus\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label type-alias\">type-alias</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1pqh1hxq7yx5mt11vbd8cj9eg\">一个表单可以有几种不同的状态。每种可能的状态都作为字符串文字返回。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/forms/FormControlStatus#description\">查看更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"type-alias-overview\">\n    <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\n    type <a href=\"api/forms/FormControlStatus\" class=\"code-anchor\">FormControlStatus</a> = 'VALID' | 'INVALID' | 'PENDING' | 'DISABLED';\n    </code-example>\n  </section>\n\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/FormControlStatus#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"emkx86ahxpg3fuayxfn4u63s0\"><strong>VALID</strong>：报告控件有效，这意味着输入值中不存在错误。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"23su2cgimk7c1l0zt97cr6r6c\"><strong>INVALID</strong>：报告控件无效，这意味着输入值中存在错误。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"76ez23uuejjrvl7lyct21ehqp\"><strong>PENDING</strong>：报告控件正在等待中，意味着异步验证正在进行，错误尚不可用于输入值。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"qvri9cp51a6l9sgtqaa6kl5s\"><strong>DISABLED</strong>：报告控件已禁用，这意味着该控件可以免于祖先的有效性或值计算。</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/AbstractControl\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/FormControlStatus#description\n - api/forms/FormControlStatus#formcontrolstatus\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/model/abstract_model.ts#L50-L66\n-->"}